1
00:00:42,850 --> 00:00:48,540
♪Flower petals have fallen,
piling as high as mortal mercilessness♪

2
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:55,410
♪Gone with the wind,
as if it has never existed♪

3
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:59,960
♪I ask for more time♪

4
00:01:00,900 --> 00:01:03,290
♪To rewrite our stories♪

5
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:09,650
♪We travel together in joys and woes♪

6
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:16,470
♪Blood bathes this entangled destiny♪

7
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:23,260
♪For the next reunion
in the troubled times♪

8
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,380
♪We tread a treacherous path♪

9
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,640
♪To find each other♪

10
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:37,600
♪Wars and bleakness,
the bright moon shines upon the city♪

11
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:40,930
♪I will offer my bravery♪

12
00:01:41,190 --> 00:01:44,380
♪Fighting relentlessly♪

13
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:47,630
♪All for no regrets♪

14
00:01:47,708 --> 00:01:51,348
♪In this life-and-death battle,
I will not back down♪

15
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:54,910
♪Withstand enduring time♪

16
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:58,130
♪Someone at the end of the world
never leaves♪

17
00:01:58,270 --> 00:02:05,210
♪I brave the grim haze
to be with you once again♪

18
00:02:05,210 --> 00:02:10,950
=Love of Nirvana=
(Based on Xiao Lou's novel of the same name)

19
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,180
=Episode 33=

20
00:02:51,390 --> 00:02:52,110
Miss Dong.

21
00:02:53,090 --> 00:02:53,680
Miss Jiang.

22
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:56,210
I visited Yu in the palace today.

23
00:02:56,248 --> 00:02:58,200
I heard from them
that your wedding was nearing.

24
00:02:58,264 --> 00:02:59,208
So I came to visit you.

25
00:03:00,632 --> 00:03:02,170
Miss Dong, I appreciate your concern.

26
00:03:03,384 --> 00:03:06,168
You want to marry into
the Lord of Jianding's Residence?

27
00:03:12,950 --> 00:03:13,720
I wish to escape.

28
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,120
His Lordship isn't the person I love.

29
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,000
And, I can't just sit idly by

30
00:03:20,370 --> 00:03:21,780
and get married for no reason.

31
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,210
Moreover,

32
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:24,960
I wish to find Master as well.

33
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:30,300
How do you intend to escape?

34
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,330
The palace is heavily guarded.

35
00:03:33,544 --> 00:03:34,890
Initially, I wanted to sneak out

36
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:37,000
(via a food waste cart.)

37
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:40,000
(But now, they're even inspecting
those carts as well.)

38
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,390
(I was thinking)

39
00:03:41,650 --> 00:03:42,590
that I would blend in

40
00:03:42,664 --> 00:03:44,440
with the crowd
and sneak out of the palace

41
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,488
on my wedding day.

42
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:50,300
Have you discussed this
with Commander Wei?

43
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:53,110
I don't wish to implicate him.

44
00:03:55,490 --> 00:03:57,170
I can't just depend on him all the time.

45
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,270
Like this?

46
00:04:01,390 --> 00:04:02,270
Slightly to the left.

47
00:04:02,344 --> 00:04:03,208
Slightly to the left...

48
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,040
That's too much.

49
00:04:05,490 --> 00:04:07,370
I think it's still slightly crooked.

50
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,120
An,

51
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:10,800
this isn't archery or needlework.

52
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,520
We don't need to be that particular.

53
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,490
Tomorrow's His Lordship's big day.

54
00:04:14,552 --> 00:04:16,088
Of course we have to be particular.

55
00:04:16,280 --> 00:04:17,390
Those who don't know any better

56
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,984
might think that you're getting married.

57
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,150
My wedding isn't as important
as His Lordship's.

58
00:04:22,210 --> 00:04:23,250
I'll remember that.

59
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,160
I'll tell your future wife about it.

60
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,480
How dare you?

61
00:04:26,536 --> 00:04:27,592
You think you're grown up?

62
00:04:27,608 --> 00:04:28,130
Try me!

63
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:28,830
Stop right there!

64
00:04:29,544 --> 00:04:29,960
Come here!

65
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:30,420
Come on!

66
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:31,128
I'll lecture you.

67
00:04:42,552 --> 00:04:44,136
- Your Lordship.
- Sorry for the ruckus.

68
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,450
You guys have done well today.

69
00:04:51,976 --> 00:04:53,208
You should go back and rest.

70
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:53,960
It's still early.

71
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,909
We still need to confirm the carpet

72
00:04:55,910 --> 00:04:58,000
Miss Jiang will step on
when she enters tomorrow.

73
00:04:58,168 --> 00:05:00,200
And the nuptial wine
that you two will be having.

74
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:02,570
And the dates and chestnuts.

75
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,150
Your Lordship,

76
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,100
I think An

77
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:06,450
has even named your child

78
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:07,100
for you.

79
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:09,600
Of course they must give birth soon

80
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:11,380
and enjoy a loving relationship
until old age.

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,420
They need to stay sweet

82
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:13,540
and harmonious as well.

83
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:18,920
(Ci.)

84
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,510
(Everything is ready.)

85
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:25,210
(I'll definitely wait until the day
you have a change of heart.)

86
00:05:30,790 --> 00:05:34,690
(Yuchun Pavilion)

87
00:05:59,864 --> 00:06:00,780
(Let me help you out.)

88
00:06:01,770 --> 00:06:02,860
I mustn't implicate you.

89
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,070
Don't worry.

90
00:06:04,136 --> 00:06:06,232
I was raised
in a prestigious family since young.

91
00:06:06,248 --> 00:06:06,984
I'm used to it.

92
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,280
I can protect myself.

93
00:06:08,450 --> 00:06:09,150
But Miss Dong...

94
00:06:09,192 --> 00:06:10,696
Moreover, the palace is heavily guarded

95
00:06:10,712 --> 00:06:11,950
and filled with rites and customs.

96
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,190
You can't escape

97
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,520
from this place alone.

98
00:06:15,690 --> 00:06:16,920
I'm not as cool

99
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,020
or as brave as you.

100
00:06:18,710 --> 00:06:20,390
But I'm willing to lend you
a helping hand.

101
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:23,660
After all, by helping you out,
I'll be helping myself out.

102
00:06:24,488 --> 00:06:26,712
I was hoping that you could
explore the world for me

103
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,660
after you leave the palace.

104
00:06:31,890 --> 00:06:32,660
Thank you.

105
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:02,250
Sir,

106
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:05,420
everything is ready.

107
00:07:32,890 --> 00:07:37,090
(Bliss)

108
00:07:51,810 --> 00:07:52,590
I'll head over there.

109
00:07:53,410 --> 00:07:54,510
(Lord of Jianding's Residence)

110
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:55,240
The ladder is here.

111
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,776
I'll hold it down for you.

112
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,420
Be careful.

113
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,200
Give it to me.

114
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:04,420
Be careful.

115
00:08:04,776 --> 00:08:05,980
(Graceful and Warm)
Is it okay?

116
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:06,504
All right.

117
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:08,650
It's okay.

118
00:08:09,970 --> 00:08:12,872
(Lord of Jianding's Residence)

119
00:08:13,144 --> 00:08:14,770
We've nurtured you guys for a long time.

120
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,090
Today

121
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:19,310
is the day for you all
to repay Madam's favor!

122
00:08:20,210 --> 00:08:20,920
Yes, ma'am!

123
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:51,210
Madam.

124
00:08:51,330 --> 00:08:52,380
Madam Yan has arrived.

125
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,480
Madam Yan,

126
00:08:59,464 --> 00:09:01,830
please blend in with
the convoy transporting the bridal gifts.

127
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:03,710
Once you enter the palace,

128
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:05,640
someone will guide you to the side hall.

129
00:09:10,090 --> 00:09:11,430
I'm afraid you cannot

130
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,860
take that sword with you.

131
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:18,090
This is my sword.

132
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,240
I never leave without it.

133
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,810
You can hide it among the bridal gifts.

134
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:28,310
You can't just enter the palace
with your sword.

135
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:06,296
The result of today rests
entirely on our shoulders.

136
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,430
You and I are different.

137
00:10:10,792 --> 00:10:12,968
We're taking
what we need from each other.

138
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:15,980
If everything proceeds smoothly,

139
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,600
you may leave with Jiang Ci

140
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,740
while I'll help Yan
to ascend the throne.

141
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,480
But if something goes wrong,

142
00:10:26,430 --> 00:10:27,840
we need to stay united.

143
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:30,670
We mustn't drag the children down.

144
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,480
Madam, you kept this painting
with you for over 30 years.

145
00:11:09,690 --> 00:11:11,720
I knew he was paranoid.

146
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:15,740
That's why I kept this painting
with me at all times.

147
00:11:16,776 --> 00:11:18,568
I merely kept it to protect myself.

148
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:39,450
It's been 30 years.

149
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:42,220
It's time for you

150
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,790
to pay the price.

151
00:11:47,848 --> 00:11:49,480
But I'm afraid His Lordship will be...

152
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,720
Since he asked for this himself,

153
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,810
he should bear the consequences.

154
00:11:58,170 --> 00:12:01,360
He has to experience the taste
of wanting but never obtaining

155
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:03,860
for him to understand

156
00:12:04,690 --> 00:12:06,430
that sacrifices have to be made

157
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:10,690
for one to achieve something remarkable.

158
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:44,110
(Minxiu Hall)

159
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:38,860
Greetings, Your Highness.

160
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:40,232
Second Young Lady Dong, please rise.

161
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,950
Your Highness, today's your wedding day.

162
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:47,190
I'm here to help you
put on the bridal makeup.

163
00:13:47,528 --> 00:13:48,690
I appreciate your intention.

164
00:13:49,450 --> 00:13:50,720
All of you may leave.

165
00:14:01,930 --> 00:14:03,710
You should change into
Jin Xin's clothing.

166
00:14:04,264 --> 00:14:06,170
I'll take you with me
and leave in a carriage.

167
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:07,930
You guys must say that you

168
00:14:08,008 --> 00:14:09,160
were coerced into assisting me

169
00:14:09,224 --> 00:14:10,639
out of the palace
as I kidnapped you.

170
00:14:10,640 --> 00:14:11,880
You guys mustn't be implicated.

171
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,590
Don't worry.

172
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:15,710
I'm better at dealing with them
than you are.

173
00:14:15,736 --> 00:14:16,760
Once you leave the palace,

174
00:14:16,792 --> 00:14:18,280
you must keep moving forward.

175
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:19,710
Do not turn back.

176
00:14:20,450 --> 00:14:21,260
Thank you.

177
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:23,690
Report this to the palace immediately

178
00:14:23,690 --> 00:14:24,950
right after I leave the palace.

179
00:14:24,950 --> 00:14:26,410
This way, they won't suspect you.

180
00:14:26,430 --> 00:14:27,220
Your Highness,

181
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:29,190
I'm afraid we'll never meet again
after this.

182
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:32,810
Go now.

183
00:14:33,070 --> 00:14:34,410
If not, it'll be too late.

184
00:15:01,272 --> 00:15:02,504
Who's leaving the palace?

185
00:15:05,304 --> 00:15:06,670
Greetings, Second Young Lady Dong.

186
00:15:06,810 --> 00:15:08,340
I felt sick all of a sudden.

187
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,480
That's why I'm heading home.

188
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:10,720
I see.

189
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:11,944
Second Young Lady Dong, please.

190
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,640
What is it?

191
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,720
I think I saw Master.

192
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,590
That's the Pei's Residence
bridal gift convoy.

193
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,760
I think they're heading toward
the side hall.

194
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:17,590
Are you sure about that?

195
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:19,460
I'll never mistake Master
for anyone else.

196
00:16:22,904 --> 00:16:23,976
You should leave first.

197
00:16:24,008 --> 00:16:24,952
I'll check the situation.

198
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,960
I'm sure Master is here to find me.

199
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,600
I can't leave her here by herself.

200
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:30,220
Moreover, I can't implicate you too.

201
00:16:31,830 --> 00:16:33,480
But this is your last chance.

202
00:16:39,816 --> 00:16:40,488
Stop right there.

203
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,000
Okay. Proceed.

204
00:16:47,336 --> 00:16:47,810
Go now.

205
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:59,290
(Side Hall, Hongtai Hall,
Imperial Palace, Qingkang)

206
00:17:25,030 --> 00:17:27,352
(Liang)

207
00:17:58,340 --> 00:18:00,090
The auspicious hour has arrived.

208
00:18:00,340 --> 00:18:02,030
Summon Her Highness!

209
00:18:03,730 --> 00:18:05,510
The auspicious hour has arrived.

210
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,880
Summon Her Highness!

211
00:18:37,090 --> 00:18:48,030
(Minxiu Hall)

212
00:18:55,270 --> 00:18:56,530
Sanlang isn't around today.

213
00:18:56,904 --> 00:18:58,100
All of you must stay alert.

214
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,730
I didn't see Madam

215
00:19:00,990 --> 00:19:02,270
when I left the residence too.

216
00:19:05,230 --> 00:19:08,860
His Majesty has arrived!

217
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,100
Greetings, Your Majesty.

218
00:19:18,010 --> 00:19:19,440
All of you may rise.

219
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:21,840
Thank you, Your Majesty,

220
00:19:23,976 --> 00:19:24,770
Begin the ceremony.

221
00:19:28,570 --> 00:19:30,570
The auspicious hour has arrived!

222
00:19:30,990 --> 00:19:33,590
Let the honorable ceremony begin!

223
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:56,160
Wait!

224
00:21:23,050 --> 00:21:23,990
I'm afraid we cannot

225
00:21:24,120 --> 00:21:25,360
proceed with today's wedding.

226
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:27,990
What happened?

227
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:32,330
Your Majesty, please pardon me.

228
00:21:32,490 --> 00:21:34,440
Assassins have snuck into the palace.

229
00:21:35,730 --> 00:21:36,570
Assassins?

230
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:38,380
Where are they?

231
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:39,840
I'm doing my best to locate them.

232
00:21:40,010 --> 00:21:42,530
Your Majesty, fellow officials,
please return for now.

233
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,970
Father, please return
to the palace immediately.

234
00:21:48,730 --> 00:21:49,600
Chief Steward Tao,

235
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:51,240
Madam Rongguo has gone to the side hall.

236
00:21:51,840 --> 00:21:52,250
This is...

237
00:21:53,700 --> 00:21:54,230
Your Majesty,

238
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:56,070
Madam Rongguo has gone to the side hall.

239
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:02,530
Wei Zhao.

240
00:22:02,620 --> 00:22:03,940
Come with me.

241
00:22:04,424 --> 00:22:05,240
Yes, Your Majesty.

242
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:16,730
Sanlang.

243
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:18,730
Wait here.

244
00:22:18,952 --> 00:22:20,216
Tell your men to get ready.

245
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,250
Your Majesty,

246
00:22:21,620 --> 00:22:22,970
I'm afraid there'll be an ambush.

247
00:22:22,990 --> 00:22:24,250
You mustn't enter the hall alone.

248
00:22:26,290 --> 00:22:27,010
Just wait here.

249
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:28,250
I'll summon you

250
00:22:28,530 --> 00:22:29,490
if there's an ambush.

251
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:32,790
Remember,

252
00:22:34,140 --> 00:22:35,270
do not let anyone in

253
00:22:36,380 --> 00:22:38,360
or out.

254
00:22:38,536 --> 00:22:39,336
Yes, Your Majesty.

255
00:22:58,310 --> 00:22:59,920
You're finally here.

256
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:01,990
Yudie,

257
00:23:02,744 --> 00:23:04,776
you should be attending
Pei Yan's wedding ceremony

258
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,550
at the main hall.

259
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,470
What are you doing here?

260
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,330
It's Yan's wedding,

261
00:23:13,230 --> 00:23:14,470
yet his father isn't around.

262
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:17,180
Your Majesty, I'm sure you know why.

263
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:18,830
You abandoned me

264
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:20,310
for the sake of imperial power.

265
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,810
Since you left me to Zijing,

266
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,230
why did you have to harm him?

267
00:23:27,830 --> 00:23:30,900
Because of you, my son and I
are isolated and helpless.

268
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,420
I was also heartbroken
about Zijing's death

269
00:23:34,940 --> 00:23:36,700
when I heard about it.

270
00:23:40,810 --> 00:23:43,490
Stop pretending.

271
00:23:44,570 --> 00:23:46,830
You may be able to deceive others,
but not me.

272
00:23:48,010 --> 00:23:51,120
The cavalries of Wei State
didn't kill Zijing.

273
00:23:51,250 --> 00:23:53,250
Your paranoia killed him.

274
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:55,590
Yudie,

275
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,810
that's just your conjecture.

276
00:23:58,470 --> 00:24:00,470
That's a baseless accusation.

277
00:24:00,536 --> 00:24:01,790
Your Majesty, did you forget?

