00:42:42,530 --> 00:42:45,530
and make you pay for what you did.

557
00:42:49,620 --> 00:42:51,760
I've abandoned plenty of things
throughout my life.

558
00:42:53,430 --> 00:42:54,450
I no longer remember them.

559
00:42:56,260 --> 00:42:57,870
But abandoning you

560
00:42:59,640 --> 00:43:01,300
is the only regret I have.

561
00:43:03,010 --> 00:43:03,700
Yudie.

562
00:43:05,090 --> 00:43:06,660
I always remembered

563
00:43:06,850 --> 00:43:08,350
your love for me.

564
00:43:08,930 --> 00:43:11,260
I knew the kind of person you were

565
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:14,970
on the first day I met you.

566
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:17,410
I gave you a choice.

567
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:21,050
We could've maintained
the same relationship

568
00:43:22,740 --> 00:43:24,820
had you made the other choice.

569
00:43:25,780 --> 00:43:27,430
But you gave up on me

570
00:43:27,910 --> 00:43:29,600
and chose Zijing instead.

571
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:33,820
You still dare to mention his name?

572
00:43:36,390 --> 00:43:38,490
It was difficult enough
for me to let go of the past

573
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:41,550
and start anew with Zijing!

574
00:43:41,550 --> 00:43:44,200
Your paranoia caused us
to be separated by life and death!

575
00:43:44,200 --> 00:43:45,620
That's why my son has no father!

576
00:43:45,620 --> 00:43:47,070
It was you!

577
00:43:47,430 --> 00:43:49,820
You've ruined my life once again!

578
00:43:56,930 --> 00:43:58,850
You've also ruined the only sentiment

579
00:44:00,120 --> 00:44:02,430
I had left of you.

580
00:44:11,850 --> 00:44:13,120
Sentiment?

581
00:44:15,430 --> 00:44:18,590
Your Majesty, I assume you
believe in your own words, right?

582
00:44:19,350 --> 00:44:21,120
Your Majesty, you didn't miss

583
00:44:21,120 --> 00:44:23,530
the moments you spent together with me.

584
00:44:23,530 --> 00:44:25,350
You merely missed

585
00:44:25,350 --> 00:44:26,990
the past version of you,

586
00:44:26,990 --> 00:44:29,800
who had still retained
a sliver of purity left.

587
00:44:31,200 --> 00:44:34,470
You thought you had feelings.

588
00:44:37,220 --> 00:44:38,220
But Xie Che,

589
00:44:38,890 --> 00:44:40,280
do you know the only kind of person

590
00:44:40,280 --> 00:44:42,590
who will fall for people like you?

591
00:44:48,430 --> 00:44:50,300
The same kind of person as you.

592
00:44:52,970 --> 00:44:54,620
I knew that you and I

593
00:44:55,050 --> 00:44:57,240
were the same kind of person
when I first met you.

594
00:44:58,350 --> 00:44:59,760
We hide our intentions away

595
00:45:00,890 --> 00:45:02,240
as we bide our time.

596
00:45:03,680 --> 00:45:04,760
When I saw you,

597
00:45:05,590 --> 00:45:07,430
it was as if
I was looking into a mirror.

598
00:45:08,200 --> 00:45:09,550
But I never expected your ambitions

599
00:45:11,070 --> 00:45:12,950
and desire

600
00:45:13,740 --> 00:45:16,550
to turn you into a monster like this.

601
00:45:17,510 --> 00:45:19,070
Winner takes all.

602
00:45:19,760 --> 00:45:20,990
I may have lost,

603
00:45:21,640 --> 00:45:23,260
but I won't let you win.

604
00:45:24,430 --> 00:45:25,200
Xie Che.

605
00:45:26,100 --> 00:45:27,510
There's no one else in the world

606
00:45:29,390 --> 00:45:31,700
who knows me better than you.

607
00:45:35,740 --> 00:45:36,970
Xie Chun.

608
00:45:38,200 --> 00:45:39,930
He's right here.

609
00:45:40,200 --> 00:45:41,832
You can only live with
a guilty conscience

610
00:45:43,050 --> 00:45:46,090
for the rest of your life
for what you did to him.

611
00:45:46,450 --> 00:45:48,350
You will never be able
to sleep in peace.

612
00:45:49,550 --> 00:45:51,760
Do you truly think that I'll spare you?

613
00:45:53,470 --> 00:45:54,530
Aren't you afraid

614
00:45:55,390 --> 00:45:58,600
that I'll make Pei Yan pay
for what you did?

615
00:45:59,120 --> 00:45:59,620
Don't forget,

616
00:46:00,410 --> 00:46:03,090
he's still kneeling
in front of my study room.

617
00:46:03,350 --> 00:46:04,350
Xie Che,

618
00:46:04,640 --> 00:46:05,820
listen.

619
00:46:06,090 --> 00:46:09,200
I won't let you manipulate me
ever again!

620
00:46:58,620 --> 00:46:59,470
I told you before.

621
00:47:01,120 --> 00:47:02,640
I'll always retain a spot for you

622
00:47:03,240 --> 00:47:05,220
in my heart.

623
00:47:06,970 --> 00:47:08,220
Your life,

624
00:47:09,090 --> 00:47:09,930
your past,

625
00:47:10,550 --> 00:47:11,450
your present,

626
00:47:12,180 --> 00:47:13,050
and your future,

627
00:47:14,090 --> 00:47:15,180
all of them are mine.

628
00:47:16,850 --> 00:47:18,100
I won't kill you,

629
00:47:19,990 --> 00:47:22,350
but I don't wish to see you again.

630
00:47:23,416 --> 00:47:24,760
You can copy and chant sutras

631
00:47:24,850 --> 00:47:27,890
in Qingxin Monastery
for the rest of your life.

632
