♪The slanting sunray refuses to leave♪

633
00:48:28,839 --> 00:48:32,189
♪The moon is fading off♪

634
00:48:33,159 --> 00:48:37,419
♪Frost on the sword, string of the bow♪

635
00:48:37,719 --> 00:48:41,599
♪Bond people together♪

636
00:48:42,169 --> 00:48:46,389
♪The wind heading north and
the wild geese returning from the south♪

637
00:48:46,389 --> 00:48:50,399
♪Who can meet again?♪

638
00:48:50,959 --> 00:48:54,909
♪Looking at the mountains far away
and seeing everything red♪

639
00:48:54,909 --> 00:48:59,149
♪Immersed in the passing years♪

640
00:48:59,379 --> 00:49:03,799
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

641
00:49:03,799 --> 00:49:07,689
♪Yet now I am left wandering
in this life♪

642
00:49:08,259 --> 00:49:12,379
♪Faint memories of the past♪

643
00:49:12,599 --> 00:49:16,449
♪All tell of parting sorrows♪

644
00:49:17,129 --> 00:49:21,369
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

645
00:49:21,609 --> 00:49:25,539
♪Amidst the wind, I suddenly look back♪

646
00:49:25,989 --> 00:49:29,979
♪The face that feels so dear to me♪

647
00:49:30,359 --> 00:49:33,799
♪Where are you now?♪

648
00:49:39,329 --> 00:49:43,719
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

649
00:49:43,719 --> 00:49:47,559
♪Looking back, it seems like a dream♪

650
00:49:48,079 --> 00:49:52,329
♪Don't forget each other
even if we're far apart♪

651
00:49:52,709 --> 00:49:56,389
♪Don't waste time♪

652
00:49:57,079 --> 00:50:01,269
♪Back then, the road seemed ordinary♪

653
00:50:01,539 --> 00:50:05,409
♪Taste all the vicissitudes of life
in a flash♪

654
00:50:06,019 --> 00:50:10,159
♪Though nothing is permanent♪

655
00:50:10,739 --> 00:50:14,189
♪I wish you well♪
